    A little about me

    Hi! My name is Nial Berry, and I am a 3D student with 2 years of experience on my belt. I like to use Autodesk Maya for modelling and Substance Painter for texturing. I have some experience with the Unity engine aswell, however I am much better at modelling.

     

    GET IN TOUCH

    Need an extra hand in a project? Need a commission? Or do you just want to learn more about me and my work?

    Hit me up and I'm sure we can work something out!


    *REGARDING COMMISSIONS*

    I am not a character/environment creator, as that's out of my field. However I can make props that will satisfy, in a fast and efficient manner. I am willing to make props, and in some case, vehicles. Please don't be offended if I turn down a request if I do not feel comfortable with it. I'm here to provide a good service, in a short timespan, at a great price.

    Thanks for submitting!
